{"tid":1715751,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[光復香港] 清算大學藍屍","createTime":"2019-11-13T07:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:38:25.000Z","uid":315761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35b3ce24e1545a93633b886d5dffff99abcb02c7","tid":1715751,"uid":315761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"雖然大學有好多黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但亦都有一班冥頑不靈既藍屍(包括本地生/nds )<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢班藍屍不但散播假消息，更會隨時向警甴篤灰，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出賣前線手足</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係大學既計時炸彈。如果要係大學持續抗爭，就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">必須清算藍屍</span></span>。況且藍屍擁護獨裁中共，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">不配在提倡自由的大學讀書</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n要分辨藍屍其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，只需要留意佢地fb/ig like 乜post, 同埋佢地平日既言行舉止就可以。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(例如可以試下扮港豬同佢地吹水，睇下佢地有無用暴徒/曱甴等字眼形容義士)<br />\n<br />\n想趕佢哋走，就要係大學營造不歡迎藍屍的氛圍。呢樣要靠各位和理非去做。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果可以既話，歡迎大家係度分享身邊大學藍屍的資料和事蹟，好讓義士有所防備，也有助日後慢慢清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子:<br />\n<br />\n[藍絲醫科生]有位hku港大未來醫生怒斥各位黃絲暴徒<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/euEuQT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/euEuQT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e0f6b8e31de4db8b62e1f236707192017d2cf22f","tid":1715751,"uid":337302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:23:00.000Z","msg":"要清算就要殺藍絲"},{"pid":"d544f01952d238054c20d862122926e7363ce344","tid":1715751,"uid":315761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f6b8e31de4db8b62e1f236707192017d2cf22f","tid":1715751,"uid":337302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:23:00.000Z","msg":"要清算就要殺藍絲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:38:25.000Z","msg":"都要先知道邊個係藍絲+審判先"}]}